21static inline isc_result_t
22fromtext_in_px(ARGS_FROMTEXT) {
23 isc_token_t token;
24 dns_name_t name;
25 isc_buffer_t buffer;
26
27 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_px);
28 REQUIRE(rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
29
30 UNUSED(type);
31 UNUSED(rdclass);
32 UNUSED(callbacks);
33
34 if (origin == NULL)
35 origin = dns_rootname;
36
37 /*
38 * Preference.
39 */
40 RETERR(isc_lex_getmastertoken(lexer, &token, isc_tokentype_number,
41 false));
42 if (token.value.as_ulong > 0xffffU)
43 RETTOK(ISC_R_RANGE);
44 RETERR(uint16_tobuffer(token.value.as_ulong, target));
45
46 /*
47 * MAP822.
48 */
49 RETERR(isc_lex_getmastertoken(lexer, &token, isc_tokentype_string,
50 false));
51 dns_name_init(&name, NULL);
52 buffer_fromregion(&buffer, &token.value.as_region);
53 RETTOK(dns_name_fromtext(&name, &buffer, origin, options, target));
54
55 /*
56 * MAPX400.
57 */
58 RETERR(isc_lex_getmastertoken(lexer, &token, isc_tokentype_string,
59 false));
60 dns_name_init(&name, NULL);
61 buffer_fromregion(&buffer, &token.value.as_region);
62 RETTOK(dns_name_fromtext(&name, &buffer, origin, options, target));
63 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
64}

66static inline isc_result_t
67totext_in_px(ARGS_TOTEXT) {
68 isc_region_t region;
69 dns_name_t name;
70 dns_name_t prefix;
71 bool sub;
72 char buf[sizeof("64000")];
73 unsigned short num;
74
75 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_px);
76 REQUIRE(rdata->rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
77 REQUIRE(rdata->length != 0);
78
79 dns_name_init(&name, NULL);
80 dns_name_init(&prefix, NULL);
81
82 /*
83 * Preference.
84 */
85 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &region);
86 num = uint16_fromregion(&region);
87 isc_region_consume(&region, 2);
88 snprintf(buf, sizeof(buf), "%u", num);
89 RETERR(str_totext(buf, target));
90 RETERR(str_totext(" ", target));
91
92 /*
93 * MAP822.
94 */
95 dns_name_fromregion(&name, &region);
96 sub = name_prefix(&name, tctx->origin, &prefix);
97 isc_region_consume(&region, name_length(&name));
98 RETERR(dns_name_totext(&prefix, sub, target));
99 RETERR(str_totext(" ", target));
100
101 /*
102 * MAPX400.
103 */
104 dns_name_fromregion(&name, &region);
105 sub = name_prefix(&name, tctx->origin, &prefix);
106 return(dns_name_totext(&prefix, sub, target));
107}

109static inline isc_result_t
110fromwire_in_px(ARGS_FROMWIRE) {
111 dns_name_t name;
112 isc_region_t sregion;
113
114 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_px);
115 REQUIRE(rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
116
117 UNUSED(type);
118 UNUSED(rdclass);
119
120 dns_decompress_setmethods(dctx, DNS_COMPRESS_NONE);
121
122 dns_name_init(&name, NULL);
123
124 /*
125 * Preference.
126 */
127 isc_buffer_activeregion(source, &sregion);
128 if (sregion.length < 2)
129 return (ISC_R_UNEXPECTEDEND);
130 RETERR(mem_tobuffer(target, sregion.base, 2));
131 isc_buffer_forward(source, 2);
132
133 /*
134 * MAP822.
135 */
136 RETERR(dns_name_fromwire(&name, source, dctx, options, target));
137
138 /*
139 * MAPX400.
140 */
141 return (dns_name_fromwire(&name, source, dctx, options, target));
142}
143
144static inline isc_result_t
145towire_in_px(ARGS_TOWIRE) {
146 dns_name_t name;
147 dns_offsets_t offsets;
148 isc_region_t region;
149
150 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_px);
151 REQUIRE(rdata->rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
152 REQUIRE(rdata->length != 0);
153
154 dns_compress_setmethods(cctx, DNS_COMPRESS_NONE);
155 /*
156 * Preference.
157 */
158 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &region);
159 RETERR(mem_tobuffer(target, region.base, 2));
160 isc_region_consume(&region, 2);
161
162 /*
163 * MAP822.
164 */
165 dns_name_init(&name, offsets);
166 dns_name_fromregion(&name, &region);
167 RETERR(dns_name_towire(&name, cctx, target));
168 isc_region_consume(&region, name_length(&name));
169
170 /*
171 * MAPX400.
172 */
173 dns_name_init(&name, offsets);
174 dns_name_fromregion(&name, &region);
175 return (dns_name_towire(&name, cctx, target));
176}

178static inline int
179compare_in_px(ARGS_COMPARE) {
180 dns_name_t name1;
181 dns_name_t name2;
182 isc_region_t region1;
183 isc_region_t region2;
184 int order;
185
186 REQUIRE(rdata1->type == rdata2->type);
187 REQUIRE(rdata1->rdclass == rdata2->rdclass);
188 REQUIRE(rdata1->type == dns_rdatatype_px);
189 REQUIRE(rdata1->rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
190 REQUIRE(rdata1->length != 0);
191 REQUIRE(rdata2->length != 0);
192
193 order = memcmp(rdata1->data, rdata2->data, 2);
194 if (order != 0)
195 return (order < 0 ? -1 : 1);
196
197 dns_name_init(&name1, NULL);
198 dns_name_init(&name2, NULL);
199
200 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata1, &region1);
201 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata2, &region2);
202
203 isc_region_consume(&region1, 2);
204 isc_region_consume(&region2, 2);
205
206 dns_name_fromregion(&name1, &region1);
207 dns_name_fromregion(&name2, &region2);
208
209 order = dns_name_rdatacompare(&name1, &name2);
210 if (order != 0)
211 return (order);
212
213 isc_region_consume(&region1, name_length(&name1));
214 isc_region_consume(&region2, name_length(&name2));
215
216 dns_name_fromregion(&name1, &region1);
217 dns_name_fromregion(&name2, &region2);
218
219 return (dns_name_rdatacompare(&name1, &name2));
220}

222static inline isc_result_t
223fromstruct_in_px(ARGS_FROMSTRUCT) {
224 dns_rdata_in_px_t *px = source;
225 isc_region_t region;
226
227 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_px);
228 REQUIRE(rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
229 REQUIRE(source != NULL);
230 REQUIRE(px->common.rdtype == type);
231 REQUIRE(px->common.rdclass == rdclass);
232
233 UNUSED(type);
234 UNUSED(rdclass);
235
236 RETERR(uint16_tobuffer(px->preference, target));
237 dns_name_toregion(&px->map822, &region);
238 RETERR(isc_buffer_copyregion(target, &region));
239 dns_name_toregion(&px->mapx400, &region);
240 return (isc_buffer_copyregion(target, &region));
241}
242
243static inline isc_result_t
244tostruct_in_px(ARGS_TOSTRUCT) {
245 dns_rdata_in_px_t *px = target;
246 dns_name_t name;
247 isc_region_t region;
248 isc_result_t result;
249
250 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_px);
251 REQUIRE(rdata->rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
252 REQUIRE(target != NULL);
253 REQUIRE(rdata->length != 0);
254
255 px->common.rdclass = rdata->rdclass;
256 px->common.rdtype = rdata->type;
257 ISC_LINK_INIT(&px->common, link);
258
259 dns_name_init(&name, NULL);
260 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &region);
261
262 px->preference = uint16_fromregion(&region);
263 isc_region_consume(&region, 2);
264
265 dns_name_fromregion(&name, &region);
266
267 dns_name_init(&px->map822, NULL);
268 RETERR(name_duporclone(&name, mctx, &px->map822));
269 isc_region_consume(&region, name_length(&px->map822));
270
271 dns_name_init(&px->mapx400, NULL);
272 result = name_duporclone(&name, mctx, &px->mapx400);
273 if (result != ISC_R_SUCCESS)
274 goto cleanup;
275
276 px->mctx = mctx;
277 return (result);
278
279 cleanup:
280 dns_name_free(&px->map822, mctx);
281 return (ISC_R_NOMEMORY);
282}
283
284static inline void
285freestruct_in_px(ARGS_FREESTRUCT) {
286 dns_rdata_in_px_t *px = source;
287
288 REQUIRE(source != NULL);
289 REQUIRE(px->common.rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
290 REQUIRE(px->common.rdtype == dns_rdatatype_px);
291
292 if (px->mctx == NULL)
293 return;
294
295 dns_name_free(&px->map822, px->mctx);
296 dns_name_free(&px->mapx400, px->mctx);
297 px->mctx = NULL;
298}

300static inline isc_result_t
301additionaldata_in_px(ARGS_ADDLDATA) {
302 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_px);
303 REQUIRE(rdata->rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
304
305 UNUSED(rdata);
306 UNUSED(add);
307 UNUSED(arg);
308
309 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
310}

312static inline isc_result_t
313digest_in_px(ARGS_DIGEST) {
314 isc_region_t r1, r2;
315 dns_name_t name;
316 isc_result_t result;
317
318 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_px);
319 REQUIRE(rdata->rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
320
321 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &r1);
322 r2 = r1;
323 isc_region_consume(&r2, 2);
324 r1.length = 2;
325 result = (digest)(arg, &r1);
326 if (result != ISC_R_SUCCESS)
327 return (result);
328 dns_name_init(&name, NULL);
329 dns_name_fromregion(&name, &r2);
330 result = dns_name_digest(&name, digest, arg);
331 if (result != ISC_R_SUCCESS)
332 return (result);
333 isc_region_consume(&r2, name_length(&name));
334 dns_name_init(&name, NULL);
335 dns_name_fromregion(&name, &r2);
336
337 return (dns_name_digest(&name, digest, arg));
338}
